## Development

```bash
git clone https://github.com/you/devpulse
cd devpulse
pip install -e ".[all,dev]"
make test
```

```bash
make dev        # install with all optional deps
make test       # run pytest
make test-cov   # run with coverage report
make clean      # remove build artifacts
```

